Thierry Neuvic https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Thierry_Neuvic 0 Thierry Neuvic (born 3 August 1970) is a French actor. He has appeared in more than 50 films and television shows since 1996. He starred in the film Code Unknown, which was selected in the 2000 Cannes Film Festival. Thierry_Neuvic ( born 3_August_1970 ) is a_French_actor .
